-- LPL Financial has not reinstated sales of RCS' REITs - LPL CEO
-- 
-- Wed Dec 10, 2014 03:02PM EST
-- None



NEW YORK, Dec 10 (Reuters) - LPL Financial Holdings <LPLA.O>, the largest independent broker-dealer in the United States, has not reinstated sales of privately traded real estate investment trusts sponsored by a unit of RCS Capital Corp <RCAP.O>, LPL Chief Executive Officer Mark Casady said Wednesday.

